  "version": 1,
  "datasetId": "characters",
  "exploreContext": "You're a junior AI designer at Gridworks, a studio that helps clients fix broken AI systems. Your newest client is Terrashift, a world-building survival game with a huge creature ecosystem. Terrashift's Explorer's Guide is supposed to warn players which creatures are dangerous, but explorers keep getting the wrong advice. The original contractor trained the model on a weak shortcut instead of real signs of danger. Your job is to inspect the old model, spot the pattern, and rebuild it.",
